	Should automatically hide all closed groups from search.
	Closed groups should be shown only through invitation link, in which the login user must be authenticated
	</p>
	
	You are logged in as <%=h current_user.login %> <%# current_user is a helper method created in application controller and available in all views. Checks whether we have a user. Suveet%>
   <table>
   	<thead>
   	<tr>
   		<th>Group Id</th><th>Name</th><th>User Id</th><th>Access</th><th>Active Level</th><th>Description</th><th>Update</th><th>Delete</th>
   	</tr>
   	</thead>
   	<tbody>
   <% @groups.each do |group| %>
   	<tr>
   	<td><%= link_to group.id, group_path(group.id)  %></td> <%# Goes to show action %>
